level.heading: Foreign corporations - Application on effective date of subchapter.
Legislative History of Law 18-378
level.text: For history of Law 18-378, see notes under § 29A-101.01.

level.heading: Effective Dates
level.text: Section 110 of the Act of Aug. 6, 1962, 76 Stat. 306, Pub. L. 87-569, provided that this chapter would take effect 180 days after Aug. 6, 1962.
